'''高氯酸镱'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为Yb(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>。在水溶液中，Yb<sup>3+</sup>可以和ClO<sub>4</sub><sup>−</sup>相互作用，形成YbClO<sub>4</sub><sup>2+</sup>，其稳定常数为4.5 × 10<sup>−2</sup>。<ref>Kasabov, G.; Genov, L.; Dukov, I. Association processes between lanthanides and perchlorate ions{{bg}}. ''Godishnik na Visshiya Khimikotekhnologicheski Institut, Sofiya'', 1978. 24 (1): 265-274. ISSN: 0489-6211.</ref>

==制备==
高氯酸镱的水合物可由[[氧化镱|氧化镱]]和在浓[[高氯酸|高氯酸]]中溶解，从溶液中结晶得到。将水合物（x H<sub>2</sub>O, x＜6）在170 °C真空处理，得到一水合物。

一水合物在175 °C的真空中脱水，可以得到''R''3''c''空间群的无水物Yb(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>3</sub>，而[[六氧化二氯|Cl<sub>2</sub>O<sub>6</sub>]]经处理得到的无水物属''P''6<sub>3</sub>/''m''空间群。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=37|issue=8|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=1998-04|pages=1776–1780|doi=10.1021/ic9712683|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ic9712683|title=Thermal Behavior and X-ray Powder Diffraction Structures of Two Polymorphic Phases of Anhydrous Yb(ClO 4 ) 3|accessdate=2020-08-30|author=Frédéric Favier, Jean-Louis Pascal, Frédérique Cunin, Andrew N. Fitch, Gavin Vaughan}}</ref>

==用途==
高氯酸镱可用作Yb(III)来源，以制备其它镱化合物。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=128|issue=42|language=en|issn=0002-7863|date=2006-10|pages=13658–13659|doi=10.1021/ja0640391|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/ja0640391|title=Anionic Rare-Earth Thiocyanate Complexes as Building Blocks for Low-Melting Metal-Containing Ionic Liquids|accessdate=2020-08-30|author=Peter Nockemann, Ben Thijs, Niels Postelmans, Kristof Van Hecke, Luc Van Meervelt, Koen Binnemans}}</ref>

